<title type="html"><![CDATA[3/4(Thu)Expert lists reasons behind Taiwan ‘s negative population growth/Mountains vs Beach-What Millennials Think(Larry]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=477&amp;p=499#p499"><![CDATA[
3/4 Expert lists reasons behind Taiwan ‘s negative population growth/Mountains vs Beach --- What Millennials Think (Host: Larry)<br /><br /><span style="color: #FF0000">Place: 丹堤咖啡, 台北市延平南路107號2樓 (MRT 西門站4號出口)<br />Agenda:<br />07:00-7:15 pm Free talk<br />7:15-7:50 pm Session 1 discussion<br />7:50-8:15 pm Presentation (At least two members of each table are invited, 2 mins / each member)<br />8:15-8:45 pm Session 2 discussion<br />8:45-9:00 pm Presentation</span><br /><br />Session 1:  Expert lists reasons behind Taiwan ‘s negative population growth<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/en/news/4101181">https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/en/news/4101181</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br />1.Taiwan’s total population showed negative growth last (2020) year, and this phenomenon may continue to deteriorate. What impact do you think will have on Taiwan’s future or society?<br />2.Experts point out that the reason for the decline in the birth rate is the falling marriage rate. Do you agree with this statement? If not, what do you think is the real reasons?<br />3.If life can be repeated, are you willing to get married and have children? Why? Do you still have the traditional idea of passing on from generation to generation?<br />4.What kind of policies or incentives do you think will make young people want to marry and have children?<br />5.If compared with your childhood, do you think the children today are very happy and fortunate? Why?<br />6.     There are more and more people who do not want to get married. Do you know the real reason? Share it with us.<br /><br /><br />Session 2:<br />Mountains vs Beach --- What Millennials Think<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.shethepeople.tv/home-top-video/mountains-vs-beaches-millennials-choice/">https://www.shethepeople.tv/home-top-vi ... ls-choice/</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions:<br />1. Do you agree with the statement that introverts prefer mountains and extroverts prefer beaches? Please share why you like it?<br />2. It is very convenient to get close to the mountains or beaches in Taiwan. What activities do you usually engage in there?<br />3. Although a person ‘s personality is introvert and extrovert, each has its advantages and disadvantages, and there is no good or bad. If you can choose, which personality do you like? Why?<br /><br /><span style="color: #FF0000">P.S.<br />1.因聚會地點是在咖啡店內，所以有低消80元喔。<br />2.參加三次後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />3.請帶著開放與熱情來參加自由的全英文會話聚會~</span><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=38674">Louie Wang</a> — Sat Feb 27, 2021 9:41 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
